{"tid":781999,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"倪晨曦怕收男友戒指","createTime":"2018-08-16T10:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T10:57:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c7fe8c277764379325d81c06861ef19e191d30","tid":781999,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:57:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180816/20477169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180816%2F20477169&d=Pl9Y0NndIBa%2F5fkSG1v2xZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=a6709b8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180816%2F20477169&h=dec54268\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180816/20477169</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月16日 <br />\n<br />\n倪晨曦怕收男友戒指<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180816/large/16ec2p7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180816%2Flarge%2F16ec2p7e.jpg&h=7d0fede3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■倪晨曦昨日生日，她表示已與男友慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倪晨曦昨日31歲生日，她與陳炳銓在將軍澳拍攝ViuTV節目《廣告女皇》時，獲大會送上蛋糕祝賀。倪晨曦開心透露早前返加拿大探家人，亦已跟男友食飯慶祝，問到男友有否送戒指？她笑說：「千祈唔好，唔需要，順其自然。」她又指家人沒有催婚，而近期看到不開心的新聞，希望大家身心健康。<br />\n<br />\n擔任製片的陳炳銓笑認奉旨望女仔，問到參賽者似女友李佳芯（Ali）會否加分？他說：「大家『質地』不同，Ali夠百搭，可以有唔同風格。」提到女友提過想要簡單的求婚經歷，陳炳銓說：「佢咁講我點兜呀？我唔浪漫㗎，一步步嚟，大家專注工作。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪、攝影：羅慧敏  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n6月捲抵押后冠還債　楊婉儀尷尬蒲頭<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n陳意涵陀B急嫁導演"}]}